@startuml PluginActivationFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Ativação de Plugin/Addon (UC001 - RF002, RF003)
actor User
participant UI
participant AddonMarket
participant PluginHost
participant WorkspaceConfig

User -> UI: Acessa Loja de Addons
UI -> AddonMarket: Listar addons disponíveis
AddonMarket -> UI: Jira, Redmine, Git, etc

User -> UI: Seleciona Addon (ex: Redmine)
UI -> AddonMarket: Instalar addon
AddonMarket -> PluginHost: Registrar plugin

User -> UI: Configurar credenciais
UI -> User: Exibe campos (URL, API Key, etc)
User -> UI: Preenche URL + API Key

UI -> PluginHost: Configurar datasource
PluginHost -> PluginHost: Validar conexão
PluginHost -> WorkspaceConfig: Salvar configuração

PluginHost -> UI: Plugin ativado
UI -> User: Addon configurado - Sincronizar?
@enduml
